table_caption: Associations between baseline glymphatic imaging markers and longitudinal changes in cognitive measures in the whole group.
table_foot: Note: Reported are estimates and p‐values from linear mixed models with random intercepts and random slopes. The fixed effect of glymphatic marker*time was interpreted as the effect on longitudinal glymphatic change. Bold and * meant corrected by FDR.Abbreviations: FW, free water; Logical Delayed, Logical Memory‐Delayed Recall; MMSE, Mini‐Mental State Exam; MoCA, Montreal Cognitive Assessment; TMT‐A, Trail Making Test‐A; TMT‐B, Trail Making Test‐B; VRFs, vascular risk factor score.
